      "address": "eth:0xC6CDE7C39eB2f0F0095F41570af89eFC2C1Ea828",
      "name": "Tether Gold MultiSig",
      "description": "Custom on-chain multisig with six signers and a confirmation threshold of three. Holds the token's `owner` role and is the `owner` of the ProxyAdmin contract. Through the token it can mint XAUt, blocklist addresses via `addToBlockedList`, and permanently destroy blocked balances via `destroyBlockedFunds`. Through the ProxyAdmin it can upgrade the token implementation to arbitrary code via `upgrade` / `upgradeAndCall` or hand off the proxy admin slot via `changeProxyAdmin`. Both the signer set and the confirmation threshold are mutable on-chain via `addOwner` / `removeOwner` / `replaceOwner` / `changeRequirement`, which the multisig can execute on itself.",
